<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 12:21:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>人工智能带动中国智能手机市场反弹，高通股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-jumps-ai-sparks-rebound-chinese-smartphone-market-2024-05-02/</link><description>周四，高通股价在盘前交易中上涨 4%，此前这家专注于智能手机的芯片制造商表示，在经历了两年的低迷之后，人工智能推动的需求出现反弹，尤其是在中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 11:26:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-jumps-ai-sparks-rebound-chinese-smartphone-market-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报告中国一周内第二次“战斗巡逻”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-second-chinese-combat-patrol-week-2024-05-02/</link><description>台湾国防部周四表示，中国一周内第二次在台湾附近进行“联合战备巡逻”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 10:59:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-second-chinese-combat-patrol-week-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储缩减量化宽松安抚情绪，日元再次上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-02/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 10:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>韩国以朝鲜威胁为由提高外交警戒级别</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-raises-diplomatic-alert-levels-citing-north-korea-threats-2024-05-02/</link><description>韩国外交部周四提高了该地区五个外交机构的恐怖主义警戒级别，理由是有情报显示朝鲜可能试图伤害其官员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:21:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-raises-diplomatic-alert-levels-citing-north-korea-threats-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>经合组织上调全球增长前景 美国表现优于其他国家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/oecd-upgrades-global-growth-outlook-us-outperforms-2024-05-02/</link><description>经合组织周四表示，由于美国经济活动富有弹性，全球经济增长速度快于几个月前的预期，而通胀与央行目标的融合速度也快于预期，并上调了展望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:05:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/oecd-upgrades-global-growth-outlook-us-outperforms-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>Hugo Boss 利润超出预期，但中国落后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hugo-boss-q1-operating-profit-beats-expectations-2024-05-02/</link><description>Hugo Boss 周四第一季度营业利润超出预期，因为该公司成功控制了成本，同时仍投资于品牌和产品以促进销售。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:46:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hugo-boss-q1-operating-profit-beats-expectations-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>安赛乐米塔尔第一季度盈利最高预测，维持展望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/arcelormittal-q1-profit-tops-expectations-2024-05-02/</link><description>全球第二大钢铁制造商安赛乐米塔尔周四公布的第一季度收益超出分析师预期，并重申预计今年中国以外的全球钢铁需求将增长 3-4%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:20:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/arcelormittal-q1-profit-tops-expectations-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员敦促中俄宣布只有人类而非人工智能控制核武器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-urges-china-russia-declare-only-humans-not-ai-control-nuclear-2024-05-02/</link><description>周四，一名美国高级官员敦促中国和俄罗斯效仿美国和其他国家的声明，即只有人类而非人工智能才能做出部署核武器的决定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:49:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-urges-china-russia-declare-only-humans-not-ai-control-nuclear-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰维持香港最优惠贷款利率于5.875%不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-keeps-best-lending-rate-hong-kong-unchanged-5875-2024-05-02/</link><description>汇丰控股周四表示，在香港事实上的央行维持通过隔夜贴现窗口收取的基本利率不变，追随美联储维持利率稳定的决定后，该公司已将香港最优惠贷款利率维持在5.875%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:27:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-keeps-best-lending-rate-hong-kong-unchanged-5875-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>渣打银行利润超出预期，费用收入增加抵消了信贷损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartered-q1-profit-rises-55-beats-estimates-2024-05-02/</link><description>渣打银行周四第一季度税前利润超出预期，增长 5.5%，其交易和财富业务收入的激增足以弥补额外的信贷损失。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartered-q1-profit-rises-55-beats-estimates-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾因南海争端召见中国外交官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-summons-chinese-diplomat-over-south-china-sea-flare-up-2024-05-02/</link><description>菲律宾周四召见一名中国外交官，抗议北京在南海争议浅滩对菲律宾船只使用高压水枪，称其为骚扰和“危险举动”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:22:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-summons-chinese-diplomat-over-south-china-sea-flare-up-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>香港央行维持关键利率不变，追踪美联储决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracks-fed-move-2024-05-02/</link><description>香港金融管理局（金管局）周四将通过隔夜贴现窗口收取的基本利率维持在 5.75% 不变，以追随美联储维持利率稳定的决定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:21:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracks-fed-move-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体报道，中国南方道路塌陷已造成 48 人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/road-collapse-southern-china-kills-36-reports-state-media-2024-05-02/</link><description>据官方媒体周四报道，中国广东省一高速公路路段塌方导致车辆滚下斜坡，死亡人数已上升至 48 人，救援工作因泥石流而受阻。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:20:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/road-collapse-southern-china-kills-36-reports-state-media-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称参加世卫大会可能很难，布林肯表示支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-may-be-hard-attend-who-assembly-blinken-offers-support-2024-05-02/</link><description>在美国催促邀请后，台湾外交部长周四表示，台湾参加今年的世界卫生组织年会将很困难，希望更多国家支持其出席。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 02:32:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-may-be-hard-attend-who-assembly-blinken-offers-support-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛选择对中国友好的马内莱为新总理</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-chooses-jeremiah-manele-new-prime-minister-2024-05-02/</link><description>周四，所罗门群岛立法者选举杰里米亚·马内莱(Jeremiah Manele)为新任总理，提升了这位前外交部长的地位，他承诺继续这个太平洋岛国的国际政策，拉近与中国的距离。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 01:39:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-chooses-jeremiah-manele-new-prime-minister-2024-05-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>